						<summary>

						<p>Stone in the village.</p>						

						<p>This is dated <hi rend="bold">Śaka 162[7], Tāraṇa, Āshāḍha ba. 5, Monday</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">1704 A.D. July 10, Monday, °54.</hi> The Śaka year was current.</p>						

						<p>Damaged. Seems to state that Sādutullā Asāri Handammīyā Sāhebu granted Ūrachintala (surnamed as Veṇkkaṭam) in Avuku-<hi rend="italic">sīma</hi> for the settlement of certain families.</p>						

						</summary>
